        <p class="parrafo col-8 col-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-6 col-sm-8">I live in a town in the south of Spain, that has the biggest reservoir in the whole region. This was very interesting to tell how it does not really matter when it comes to water, no matter if there is enough or not. This project revolves around this idea: businesses that cannot live without water (there are greenhouses in the surroundings of Doñana’s National Park and that take water from it or olive trees being watered to power their perfomance) and how the government does nothing to change this situation.</p>
